e end of the hit calculation (just like the inherent damage bonus that each melees gets with their main hand.)<br><br>SO, that said, the fungus is still your best mainhand weapon. 10/21 is your fastest weapon (and remember you want your fastest weapon in mainhand so that the damage bonus gets applied as often as possible).<br><br>For the offhand, it's gonna depend if you're hasted or not. If you're hasted, take the BBoT cause you'll probably be able to proc a lot and hold aggro that way. However, if you're not hasted, you're not gonna proc very often with a 22 delay weapon, so go for the superior damage of the 12/23 (pretty nice ratio actually).<br><br>When xping, always take the 12/23 as the proc off the 9/22 will not make up for the extra damage.<br><br> <p>Shelrabbi Hassida<BR>Tallon Zek<BR>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=216910<BR><br>"Beer is the path to the dark side. Beer leads to drunkeness. Drunkeness leads to beer goggles. Beer goggles lead to dirty womanOnce you get a dirty woman on your jock, forever will she dominate your destiny. Besides, Whiskey is the drink of the true jedi." -Yoda</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/udumeshuhlbelk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dumesh UhlBelk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 118<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/30/02 1:18:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3360.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://personal.bhm.bellsouth.net/bhm/w/i/wilsonua/DumStare.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Need some we